# Billing is NOT wired up yet. routes/child.py tracks usage minutes and
# computes the £1.50/hr overage past the included 15 hours/month, and
# routes/parent.py shows it on the dashboard — but nothing actually
# charges a card. Connect your provider of choice (Stripe metered
# billing is the natural fit) before relying on this for real money.
